## Integration with Audit Commands

This rule should be referenced by all audit commands:

- `audit-security.md` - Security audit reports
- `audit-database.md` - Database audit reports
- `audit-access-control.md` - Access control audit reports
- `audit-docs.md` - Documentation audit reports
- `audit-readmes.md` - README audit reports
- `full-project-health-check.md` - Combined health check reports

**Command Integration:**
- Commands should check for this rule and follow its standards
- Commands should create `/docs/audit/` if missing
- Commands should use standardized naming convention
- Commands should include report location in output

